<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.8">
<l>teyvaṅkā ḷeṉceykē ṉōriravē ḻūḻiyāy</l>
<l>meyvantu niṉṟeṉa tāvi melivikkuṅ</l>
<l>kaivanta cakkaratteṉ kaṇṇaṉum vārāṉā</l>
<l>ṟaivanta taṇṭeṉṟal veñcuṭariṟ ṟāṉaṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O gods, what will I do? One night come [and] standing</l>
<l>there bodily as seven aeons, weakens my soul.</l>
<l>My Kaṇṇaṉ too will not come, with [his] successful discus.</l>
<l>The cool south wind that grates will kill [me] like the hot glow [of the sun].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
